msgid ""
"Our vision is for Saaf to become the leading destination for customized "
"handmade work in Saudi Arabia, opening real opportunities for talented "
"artisans and strengthening the digital presence of local products through "
"quality, authenticity, and creativity."
msgstr ""
"رؤيتنا أن تصبح سعف الوجهة الرائدة للأعمال اليدوية المخصصة في المملكة العربية"
